---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import StudioTeam from '../components/StudioTeam.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Studio" description="Meet the Parallax Studios team. 10 specialists. 14 games. Every angle.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <span class="text-xs font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] tracking-widest text-[var(--color-phosphor)] block mb-4">THE STUDIO</span>
      <h1 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        Every angle. Every voice.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Parallax Studios is built on a simple idea: the best game design happens when
        specialists with strong opinions argue productively. Our team of 10 named agents
        each brings a distinct philosophy, a signature question, and the scars of past
        projects that inform every decision.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats bar -->
  <section class="px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[var(--color-void-light)] p-6 text-center">
        <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-phosphor)]">14</span>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-dim)] font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mt-2 tracking-wider">GAME CONCEPTS</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[var(--color-void-light)] p-6 text-center">
        <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-amber)]">84</span>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-dim)] font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mt-2 tracking-wider">DESIGN DOCS</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[var(--color-void-light)] p-6 text-center">
        <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-bone)]">700K+</span>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-dim)] font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mt-2 tracking-wider">WORDS WRITTEN</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[var(--color-void-light)] p-6 text-center">
        <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl font-bold" style="color: #ff006e;">10</span>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-dim)] font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] mt-2 tracking-wider">SPECIALISTS</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team roster -->
  <StudioTeam />

  <!-- Process section -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <span class="text-xs font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] tracking-widest text-[var(--color-phosphor)] block mb-4">THE PROCESS</span>
      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">
        From pitch to production-ready
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-phosphor)]/20 bg-[var(--color-phosphor)]/5 flex items-center justify-center font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-[var(--color-phosphor)] text-sm font-bold">
            01
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-lg font-bold mb-2">The Pitch</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
              REED, NOVA, and HYPE collaborate on the foundational document. The hook, the loop, the heart, and the market position — defined in a single session. If it can't stop a scroll, it doesn't leave this phase.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-amber)]/20 bg-[var(--color-amber)]/5 flex items-center justify-center font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-[var(--color-amber)] text-sm font-bold">
            02
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-lg font-bold mb-2">Game Design Document</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
              REED leads the deep dive. Core loops at four timescales, mechanics with player-facing and system-facing descriptions, systems interaction maps, progression curves, and the essential question: what could make this unfun?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-[var(--color-bone)] text-sm font-bold">
            03
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-lg font-bold mb-2">Narrative Bible</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
              NOVA builds the world. The wound, the geography, the characters (desire/need/wound/lie/arc), the tone guide, and the lore hierarchy from need-to-know to never-told.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-phosphor)]/20 bg-[var(--color-phosphor)]/5 flex items-center justify-center font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-[var(--color-phosphor)] text-sm font-bold">
            04
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-lg font-bold mb-2">Art, Sound & Tech</h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
              PIXEL defines the visual identity. ECHO designs the sonic palette. BYTE architects the technical foundation. Three specialists, three documents, one cohesive vision.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy section -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">
        Our philosophy
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Every game we design starts with a question nobody else is asking.
          What if a factory had feelings? What if a Broadway show was a bet?
          What if the 2000s internet was alive again?
        </p>
        <p>
          We don't chase genres. We chase industries — and find the game hiding inside each one.
        </p>
        <p class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl text-[var(--color-bone)] font-medium italic">
          "14 games. 14 industries. Every angle."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
